msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_whatsnew.xml:573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A SCSI initiator can issue SCSI reservations for a shared storage device, "
"which locks out SCSI initiators on other servers from accessing the device. "
"These reservations persist across SCSI resets that might happen as part of "
"the SCSI exception handling process."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_whatsnew.xml:579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following are possible scenarios where SCSI reservations would be useful:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_whatsnew.xml:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
