"against administrator errors where a LUN is attempted to be added to one "
"server but it is already in use by another server, which might result in "
"data corruption. SAN zoning is typically used to prevent this type of error."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_whatsnew.xml:594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a high-availability environment with failover set up, persistent SCSI "
"reservations help protect against errant servers connecting to SCSI devices "
"that are reserved by other servers."
msgstr ""

