"RAID 0, 1, 10, 5, and 6. The installer can detect RAID arrays and whether "
"the platform RAID capabilities are enabled. If multipath RAID is enabled in "
"the platform BIOS for Intel Matrix Storage Manager, it offers options for "
"DMRAID, MDRAID (recommended), or none. The <filename>initrd</filename> was "
"also modified to support assembling BIOS-based RAID arrays."
msgstr ""

